# Fire TV / Amazon update & telemetry blocklist for Pi-hole
# Purpose: reduce/stop Fire OS updates and device telemetry via DNS blocking
# Notes:
# - Blocking updates may impact some Amazon services on certain devices.
# - Do NOT add broad amazon domains; keep it specific.

# --- Firmware / software update endpoints ---
softwareupdates.amazon.com
updates.amazon.com
fireos.amazon.com

# --- Download/CDN endpoints often used by system components ---
amzdigitaldownloads.edgesuite.net
amzdigital-a.akamaihd.net.

# --- Device metrics / telemetry ---
device-metrics.amazon.com
device-metrics-us.amazon.com

# --- Device capability / captive / service endpoints sometimes tied to update checks ---
dcape-na.amazon.com

# --- (Optional) account API; can impact sign-in/activation in some cases ---
# api.amazon.com

